{"tid":1685782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10.31  高等法院法治確實已死","createTime":"2019-10-31T17:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T22:34:29.000Z","uid":87915,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0c0549f28b5f16601e575848b1474c6e0b9c5d","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"雖然相比起四個月發生嘅事，10月31日 是值得大家「紀念」 嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港黑警 正式第一次將一場公眾活動，無衝擊情況下，定性為非法集結<br />\n<br />\n~&gt; 可見大家聖誕可以盡慶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 律政司 申請違反基本法 第二十七條 禁制令<br />\n<br />\n第二十七條 <br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 高等法院 批出 違反基本法 第二十七條 禁制令 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">並寫出違反香港核心價值判詞</span><br />\n<br />\n「高浩文法官處理禁制令表示，鑒於近日有警員受傷及財物被毀壞，以及網上平台匿名及易於接觸，認為在網上平台上威脅使用暴力的言論，在示威者的暴力或破壞行為中扮演重要角色，如果不加以限制，相關暴力不會停止。法庭頒下禁制令目的之一是要告知大眾，網上言論並非沒有法律後果，雖然批下臨時禁制令會損害表達自由，但表達自由並非絕對，要有妥協及平衡。法庭認為申請方理據具說服力，頒下臨時禁制令亦符合比例。」<br />\n<br />\n幫呢位高等法院 法官總結核心思想：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我明知會損害言論自由都要做<br />\n因為如果繼續有言論自由 暴力都唔會停止</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">法官呢個係乜撚嘢邏輯？<br />\n無言論自由可以停止暴力？邊段歷史可以證明？仲要用法庭權力去講出嚟？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雖然大家成日話法治已死，而今日係成個司法界已死，而係有真憑實據</span>"},{"pid":"801968944f17afcfc6aa1b22864749118e762403","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ccf41f5fa1b227fd6f8c02a248e5d3fb99bada4","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4229d4cc58a3ec94c7f2955b62e997c9d59fc31f","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffbb6a8d42d4e21555340c4ac0fdeafffd6b1fe8","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25e0336a36b4315d66cee5cb5d35422905c8fab3","tid":1685782,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8a905ee42adc13a4fdaf656bf4fc4b47d82a3ff","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"法庭898"},{"pid":"73c8b22b89313e0f16ef1d25aac8f44afb25fa0e","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"法官898"},{"pid":"d2b6c97298b4cdbde31b2a06bdcfd8afcbf941ad","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"香港死咗啦"},{"pid":"6722977f3b7d17497558583b68712364dc841c98","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"香港玩完啦"},{"pid":"eecfe26c56541a79e481cf7d653d9352e0c82021","tid":1685782,"uid":4787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"730bb6ee8d24d9c5b36c95e7af937f1e0b27d033","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:54:45.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"8656819da3a7a3bd7d7c04ce27e86f9ae4eb283f","tid":1685782,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eba2f2f102c86079ee27a3b18c567553d92d5e9","tid":1685782,"uid":84123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"只會令到香港人更多出嚟反抗"},{"pid":"ca2622896d0549e1fb3039c6d32bff30284eade8","tid":1685782,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"香港人只會仲嬲"},{"pid":"4f9a8d46db172865a792f744448646910d6e8910","tid":1685782,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:57:39.000Z","msg":"同共產黨講法治？笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3510d03